# Documentation

## Purpose

Documentation must match implementation. Auto-triggered in pipeline phase per `07-workflow-invocation.mdc`.

## Update When

- Features or sections change
- Architecture or folder structure changes
- Public API or exported utilities change
- Developer workflow changes

## Locations

| Path | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `AGENTS.md` | Agent system handbook |
| `PROJECT_STRUCTURE.md` | Structure, section IDs, utilities |
| `docs/VERSIONING.md` | Release and deploy workflow |
| `design-reviews/` | Design notes (historical) |

## Rules

- Do not create markdown files unless requested
- Verify every path and filename mentioned exists
- Section IDs must match `Navigation.tsx` hash links
- Tech versions must match `package.json`
- Update `PROJECT_STRUCTURE.md` when architecture changes (currently outdated)

## Routing

Documentation phase → **Documentation Specialist** (see `06-role-routing.mdc`)

## Validation

After doc updates, verify facts against live code before Orchestrator approval.
